|4 |  │   ├─HASH JOIN            |                        |1       |6           |
|5 |  │   │ ├─SUBPLAN SCAN       |VIEW2                   |1       |3           |
|6 |  │   │ │ └─HASH DISTINCT    |                        |1       |3           |
|7 |  │   │ │   └─TABLE FULL SCAN|CHILD_SUBQUERY1_t1(idx7)|1       |3           |
|8 |  │   │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |SUBQUERY1_t2            |2       |3           |
|9 |  │   └─MATERIAL             |                        |1       |3           |
|10|  │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |SUBQUERY1_t1            |1       |3           |
|11|  └─HASH JOIN                |                        |2       |14          |
|12|    ├─TABLE FULL SCAN        |table1                  |1       |3           |
|13|    └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |table2                  |28      |4           |
=================================================================================
